OL,3,CAppeal renewed in murder of mother
OL,4,Cafter David Bowie concert 39 years ago
OL,6,FA renewed appeal has been issued in
OL,7,Fthe case of a young mother who was
OL,8,Fmurdered after going to a David Bowie
OL,9,Fconcert at Slane Castle 39 years ago.
OL,11,FAntoinette Smith disappeared after she
OL,12,Fand a friend attended the concert in
OL,13,FCo Meath on Saturday July 11 1987.
OL,15,FThe remains of the 27-year-old mother
OL,16,Fof two were found nine months later in
OL,17,Fa drain on the Glendoo Mountain in Co
OL,18,FWicklow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
