OL,3,CAppeal renewed in murder of mother
OL,4,Cafter David Bowie concert 39 years ago
OL,6,FAfter the gig, they returned to Dublin
OL,7,Fby bus, arriving in Parnell Square at
OL,8,Faround 11pm, and went to the nearby La
OL,9,FMirage Discotheque.
OL,11,FWhile in the club they met two men
OL,12,Fthat they knew.
OL,14,FThey remained in their company until
OL,15,Fthey all left shortly after 2am.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
