OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1783772364
OL,3,CAppeal renewed in murder of mother
OL,4,Cafter David Bowie concert 39 years ago
OL,6,FMs Smith's friend parted company with
OL,7,Fthe other three after they left the
OL,8,Fclub while Ms Smith and the two men
OL,9,Fremained for some time before all
OL,10,Fthree walked a short distance to a
OL,11,Ftaxi rank on O'Connell Street.
OL,13,FGardai said the men got a taxi to the
OL,14,FBallymun area while Ms Smith continued
OL,15,Fto walk by the Gresham Hotel on
OL,16,FO'Connell Street towards O'Connell
OL,17,FStreet Bridge.
OL,19,FShe was subsequently reported missing
OL,20,Fby her husband.
