OL,3,CAppeal renewed in murder of mother
OL,4,Cafter David Bowie concert 39 years ago
OL,6,FMs Smith's children Lisa and Rachel
OL,7,Fwere aged seven and four respectively
OL,8,Fwhen their mother disappeared 39 years
OL,9,Fago.
OL,11,FGardai at Bray Garda Station have used
OL,12,Fthe anniversary to renew their appeal
OL,13,Fto the public for assistance.
OL,15,FThey encouraged anyone with
OL,16,Finformation to come forward, as they
OL,17,Fsaid that relationships and
OL,18,Fassociations people may have had
OL,19,Fdecades ago could now have changed.
